[Invasoid Round 2 / Kei / Daytime] It seems to have become
somewhat famous. Shall I secretly peek at people's reactions
in crowded places?

Everyone became a magical girl for their own reasons. I
wonder why I started my activities as a magical girl?

[Mr. Hypnosis 3rd Round / K1 / Kei / Daytime]
Today's fortune: If you feel complicated emotions, it might be a good idea to talk to a long-time friend.

After the battle, I heard a meaningful word from Black
Muscle. My heart feels unsettled.

[Black Muscle 4 Round / K2] I will definitely settle the
score with that muscle Dharma.

After learning the truth about the villains, I was troubled
for a while.

description:
[K3, R3, N5, M3, T4 / Levantia / Night]
When I had complex worries, I used to go to a high place and watch the sunset,
but I wonder where that high place I can go to is.

It's meaningless to regret now.
I have to do what I can.
name: K5: Finally, overcoming temptation.

description:
I intend to continue being a magical girl even after
finishing all the stories.

can find someone who knows how to increase popularity?
I was able to hear Matsuo's thoughts on streaming.

[Black Muscle 3 Round / M1 / Levantia] It seems that famous
YouTubers can make a living from advertising revenue... If
that's the case, then maybe I can too...?

Thanks to Sherbet-chan, I learned about Matsuo's past
activities. He wasn't a popular YouTuber like he is now.

description:
[Black Muscle 4 Round / M2 / Kei / Night] I don't have the
talent to explore someone's past... But weren't there any

Emerging victorious in a 5-round battle against Black
Muscle, she sealed his wicked heart.

Even though all of our plans were ruined, Reina reassured me
that she was okay.
